:"2019-10-14T15:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條友JM9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:39:36.000Z","msg":"屌你真心有病，啲台灣人以為梁文道係香港主流聲音就仆街"},{"pid":"4bd8ff9993ab85f41a4f733e36b25c78de8f247c","tid":1654492,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"6月之後香港人已經唔再需要自稱精英教人做野，死開啦"},{"pid":"84c3836b123db52fb317dddffcdf6ca336e6e787","tid":1654492,"uid":30209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bd8ff9993ab85f41a4f733e36b25c78de8f247c","tid":1654492,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"6月之後香港人已經唔再需要自稱精英教人做野，死開啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:40:52.000Z","msg":"巴打講得好，仆街梁文道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffaf7c3d516f17d737178af3e571f57d0d3f1a17","tid":1654492,"uid":30209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:42:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">梁文道死全家</span></span>"},{"pid":"a5fd4a24da9e14be927f032bb128c0db7bb02203","tid":1654492,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:42:43.000Z","msg":"到今日仲講反送中已經知係on9 仔"},{"pid":"e241f0ef8e856a5cfe1d86c3722e9a569a795d35","tid":1654492,"uid":226640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T15:43:32.000Z","msg":"呢個文妓 一早係中國扮文人賺到fatfat啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}